{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01JdVXM1bCNFzc4hAowBb3Vf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01FyHTqs3G1drAHP3genqwvh","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"gh pr create --base main --head backflow/bf_01KKRT0MX4QWM9SEF1QMVHXMEN --title \"[backflow] Add recovering status for tasks orphaned by server restart\" --body \"$(cat <<'EOF'\n## Summary\n\n- Adds a `recovering` task status to handle tasks orphaned when the server restarts while they are `running` or `provisioning`\n- On startup, `recoverOnStartup()` transitions orphaned tasks to `recovering`, restores the in-memory `o.running` counter, and fixes up instance `RunningContainers` counts\n- Each tick, `monitorRecovering()` inspects containers and resolves recovering tasks: promotes back to `running` (container still alive), calls `handleCompletion` (container exited), or re-queues to `pending` (container/instance gone)\n- Adds `task.recovering` webhook event and allows cancelling recovering tasks via `DELETE /tasks/{id}`\n\n## Changed files\n\n- `internal/models/task.go` — Add `TaskStatusRecovering` constant\n- `internal/notify/webhook.go` — Add `EventTaskRecovering` event type\n- `internal/orchestrator/orchestrator.go` — Add `recoverOnStartup()`, `monitorRecovering()`, `requeueRecoveringTask()` methods\n- `internal/api/handlers.go` — Allow cancelling recovering tasks\n- `internal/orchestrator/recovery_test.go` — New tests covering all recovery paths\n- `internal/models/task_test.go` — Add recovering to non-terminal status test\n- `CLAUDE.md`, `docs/schema.md` — Document new status and webhook event\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [x] All existing tests pass (`go test ./...`)\n- [x] `go vet ./...` clean\n- [x] New tests cover: no orphans, running orphans, provisioning orphans, mixed orphans, re-queue (was running), re-queue (was provisioning), container still running, container exited\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1","description":"Create pull request","timeout":30000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":428,"cache_read_input_tokens":81451,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":428,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":19,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4aa0ce57-5476-4987-a635-a74810c9f869","uuid":"4a7e5823-0584-4700-bf2a-7138eaee33d9"}
